Title: The Titans
Plot: Gabrielle fools around with an ancient scroll and releases three Titans from centuries of captivity. Once again, Xena must save a village from destruction. Gabrielle also finds time for love.
GuestStars: Mark Raffety, Amanda Tollemache, Edward Campbell, Andy Anderson, Paolo Rotondo, Syd Mannion, David Mackie, Jack Dacey, Sian Hughes, Peter Morgan, Maggie Tarver, Simon Cameron, Tania Anderson, Julianne Evans
